OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1777993871
OL,3,CMan dies after being hit by car on A75
OL,4,Cat 3am
OL,6,FA 43-year-old man has died after being
OL,7,Fhit by a car on the A75 in Dumfries.
OL,9,FThe pedestrian was involved in a
OL,10,Fcollision at around 3am on Sunday 3
OL,11,FMay on the A75 between the Lockerbie
OL,12,FRoad roundabout and the A701.
OL,14,FEmergency services attended but he was
OL,15,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,17,FThe silver Ford Fiesta subsequently
OL,18,Fcrashed into a lorry in the other
OL,19,Fdirection and no other serious
OL,20,Finjuries have been reported.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
