OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1777993871
OL,3,CMan dies after being hit by car on A75
OL,4,Cat 3am
OL,6,FPolice Scotland Sergeant Wayne
OL,7,FCarnochan said: "Our thoughts remain
OL,8,Fwith the family and friends of the man
OL,9,Fwho died at this extremely difficult
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,F"Our enquiries into the crash are
OL,13,Fongoing and we'd ask anyone who
OL,14,Fwitnessed the crash, or saw the man or
OL,15,Feither vehicle prior, to come forward
OL,16,Fand speak with officers.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
